Description_lang: Engorged on essence. Upon death or reaching 20 applications, the caster explodes, inflicting Shadow damage to all nearby enemies. The damage inflicted increases based on the number of applications of $@spellname321402.
AuraDescription_lang: At 20 applications or upon death, casts $@spellname321401.Damage of $@spellname321401 increased by applications of $@spellname321402.
